<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Surprise ❤️</title>
  <style>
    body {
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #ffe0e9, #ffc2d1);
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      flex-direction: column;
      min-height: 100vh;
      color: #e91e63;
      text-align: center;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 3rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.5em;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      max-width: 600px;
    }

    .emojis {
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin: 1em 0;
      animation: float 3s infinite ease-in-out;
    }

    @keyframes float {
      0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
      50% { transform: translateY(-10px); }
    }

    .heart {
      font-size: 5rem;
      animation: pulse 1.5s infinite;
    }

    @keyframes pulse {
      0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); }
      50% { transform: scale(1.2); }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="heart">❤️</div>
  <h1>I love you! 💖</h1>
  <div class="emojis">😍🥰😘💋💞💕💓💗💖</div>
  <p>
    You're my sunshine 🌞, my favorite person 🧸, my everything 🌍.<br>
    I love you more than words can express. 💌<br><br>
    Te amo 💘<br>
    Je t’aime 🌹<br>
    Ich liebe dich 🫶<br>
    Ti amo 🌟<br>
    사랑해 ❤️<br>
    मैं तुमसे प्यार करता हूँ 💕<br>
    Eu te amo 💑<br><br>
    Forever yours 💍
  </p>
  <div class="emojis">🌈✨🌸🌷🌹🌺🌼</div>
</body>
</html>
